{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":594,"text":"How many of you have checked your email today?"},{"time":3133,"text":"Come on, raise your hands."},{"time":5029,"text":"How many of you are checking it right now?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":7160,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":8718,"text":"And how about finances? Anybody check that today?"},{"time":11218,"text":"Credit card, investment account?"},{"time":13706,"text":"How about this week?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":17659,"text":"Now, how about your household energy use?"},{"time":20776,"text":"Anybody check that today?"},{"time":22714,"text":"This week? Last week?"},{"time":26866,"text":"A few energy geeks spread out across the room."},{"time":29994,"text":"It's good to see you guys."},{"time":32563,"text":"But the rest of us -- this is a room filled with people"},{"time":35798,"text":"who are passionate about the future of this planet,"},{"time":38780,"text":"and even we aren't paying attention"},{"time":40611,"text":"to the energy use that's driving climate change."},{"time":43571,"text":"The woman in the photo with me is Harriet."},{"time":46226,"text":"We met her on our first family vacation."},{"time":48763,"text":"Harriet's paying attention to her energy use,"},{"time":51125,"text":"and she is decidedly not an energy geek."},{"time":53985,"text":"This is the story of how Harriet came to pay attention."}]},{"cues":[{"time":59224,"text":"This is coal,"},{"time":61253,"text":"the most common source of electricity on the planet,"},{"time":64610,"text":"and there's enough energy in this coal"},{"time":67834,"text":"to light this bulb for more than a year."},{"time":71786,"text":"But unfortunately, between here and here,"},{"time":73857,"text":"most of that energy is lost to things"},{"time":75289,"text":"like transmission leakage and heat."},{"time":78174,"text":"In fact, only 10 percent ends up as light."},{"time":81753,"text":"So this coal will last a little bit more than a month."},{"time":85761,"text":"If you wanted to light this bulb for a year,"},{"time":88370,"text":"you'd need this much coal."},{"time":93408,"text":"The bad news here is that, for every unit of energy we use,"},{"time":96452,"text":"we waste nine."},{"time":98525,"text":"That means there's good news,"},{"time":100156,"text":"because for every unit of energy we save,"},{"time":102739,"text":"we save the other nine."},{"time":106004,"text":"So the question is, how can we get the people in this room"},{"time":111300,"text":"and across the globe to start paying attention"},{"time":114266,"text":"to the energy we're using,"},{"time":116352,"text":"and start wasting less of it?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":119328,"text":"The answer comes from a behavioral science experiment"},{"time":121715,"text":"that was run one hot summer, 10 years ago,"},{"time":125096,"text":"and only 90 miles from here,"},{"time":127232,"text":"in San Marcos, California."},{"time":130608,"text":"Graduate students put signs on every door in a neighborhood,"},{"time":133289,"text":"asking people to turn off their air conditioning"},{"time":136110,"text":"and turn on their fans."},{"time":138320,"text":"One quarter of the homes received a message that said,"},{"time":140608,"text":"did you know you could save 54 dollars a month this summer?"},{"time":142926,"text":"Turn off your air conditioning, turn on your fans."},{"time":144744,"text":"Another group got an environmental message."},{"time":146578,"text":"And still a third group got a message about"},{"time":148667,"text":"being good citizens, preventing blackouts."},{"time":151347,"text":"Most people guessed that money-saving message would work best of all."},{"time":155064,"text":"In fact, none of these messages worked."},{"time":157677,"text":"They had zero impact on energy consumption."},{"time":160533,"text":"It was as if the grad students hadn't shown up at all."}]},{"cues":[{"time":164654,"text":"But there was a fourth message,"},{"time":166474,"text":"and this message simply said,"},{"time":168597,"text":"\"When surveyed, 77 percent of your neighbors"},{"time":172507,"text":"said that they turned off their air conditioning and turned on their fans."},{"time":174997,"text":"Please join them. Turn off your air conditioning"},{"time":176802,"text":"and turn on your fans.\""},{"time":178063,"text":"And wouldn't you know it, they did."},{"time":180760,"text":"The people who received this message"},{"time":182714,"text":"showed a marked decrease in energy consumption"},{"time":185236,"text":"simply by being told what their neighbors were doing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":188647,"text":"So what does this tell us?"},{"time":190347,"text":"Well, if something is inconvenient,"},{"time":192564,"text":"even if we believe in it,"},{"time":194553,"text":"moral suasion, financial incentives, don't do much to move us --"},{"time":198431,"text":"but social pressure, that's powerful stuff."},{"time":202101,"text":"And harnessed correctly, it can be a powerful force for good."},{"time":205719,"text":"In fact, it already is."}]},{"cues":[{"time":207884,"text":"Inspired by this insight, my friend Dan Yates and I"},{"time":210516,"text":"started a company called Opower."},{"time":212692,"text":"We built software and partnered with utility companies"},{"time":215161,"text":"who wanted to help their customers save energy."},{"time":217964,"text":"We deliver personalized home energy reports"},{"time":221030,"text":"that show people how their consumption"},{"time":222748,"text":"compares to their neighbors in similar-sized homes."},{"time":225620,"text":"Just like those effective door hangers,"},{"time":227860,"text":"we have people comparing themselves to their neighbors,"},{"time":230324,"text":"and then we give everyone targeted recommendations"},{"time":232840,"text":"to help them save."},{"time":234490,"text":"We started with paper, we moved to a mobile application,"},{"time":236796,"text":"web, and now even a controllable thermostat,"},{"time":239725,"text":"and for the last five years we've been running"},{"time":241742,"text":"the largest behavioral science experiment in the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":246145,"text":"And it's working."},{"time":247809,"text":"Ordinary homeowners and renters have saved"},{"time":249906,"text":"more than 250 million dollars on their energy bills,"},{"time":253046,"text":"and we're just getting started."},{"time":254559,"text":"This year alone, in partnership with more than 80 utilities"},{"time":257819,"text":"in six countries, we're going to generate"},{"time":260073,"text":"another two terawatt hours of electricity savings."}]},{"cues":[{"time":263225,"text":"Now, the energy geeks in the room know two terawatt hours,"},{"time":265266,"text":"but for the rest of us, two terawatt hours"},{"time":267305,"text":"is more than enough energy to power every home"},{"time":270644,"text":"in St. Louis and Salt Lake City combined"},{"time":273938,"text":"for more than a year."},{"time":275506,"text":"Two terawatt hours, it's roughly half"},{"time":277472,"text":"what the U.S. solar industry produced last year."},{"time":280058,"text":"And two terawatt hours? In terms of coal,"},{"time":283649,"text":"we'd need to burn 34 of these wheelbarrows"},{"time":286806,"text":"every minute around the clock every day for an entire year"},{"time":290802,"text":"to get two terawatt hours of electricity."},{"time":292906,"text":"And we're not burning anything."},{"time":294223,"text":"We're just motivating people to pay attention"},{"time":295951,"text":"and change their behavior."}]},{"cues":[{"time":298964,"text":"But we're just one company, and this is just"},{"time":301254,"text":"scratching the surface."},{"time":303391,"text":"Twenty percent of the electricity in homes is wasted,"},{"time":306956,"text":"and when I say wasted, I don't mean that people have"},{"time":308960,"text":"inefficient lightbulbs. They may."},{"time":312313,"text":"I mean we leave the lights on in empty rooms,"},{"time":315457,"text":"and we leave the air conditioning on when nobody's home."},{"time":318487,"text":"That's 40 billion dollars a year wasted"},{"time":321571,"text":"on electricity that does not contribute to our well-being"},{"time":324820,"text":"but does contribute to climate change."},{"time":327467,"text":"That's 40 billion -- with a B --"},{"time":329587,"text":"every year in the U.S. alone."},{"time":331870,"text":"That's half our coal usage right there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":335235,"text":"Now thankfully, some of the world's best material scientists"},{"time":338007,"text":"are looking to replace coal with sustainable resources"},{"time":341513,"text":"like these,"},{"time":342651,"text":"and this is both fantastic and essential."},{"time":346149,"text":"But the most overlooked resource to get us"},{"time":348187,"text":"to a sustainable energy future, it isn't on this slide."},{"time":351733,"text":"It's in this room. It's you, and it's me."},{"time":356389,"text":"And we can harness this resource"},{"time":359073,"text":"with no new material science"},{"time":360910,"text":"simply by applying behavioral science."},{"time":364102,"text":"We can do it today, we know it works,"},{"time":366186,"text":"and it will save us money right away."}]},{"cues":[{"time":369914,"text":"So what are we waiting for?"},{"time":372665,"text":"Well, in most places, utility regulation"},{"time":375392,"text":"hasn't changed much since Thomas Edison."},{"time":379708,"text":"Utilities are still rewarded when their customers"},{"time":382638,"text":"waste energy."},{"time":384202,"text":"They ought to be rewarded for helping their customers save it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":388005,"text":"But this story is much more than about household energy use."},{"time":391411,"text":"Take a look at the Prius."},{"time":393473,"text":"It's efficient not only because Toyota invested in material science"},{"time":396495,"text":"but because they invested in behavioral science."},{"time":398970,"text":"The dashboard that shows drivers how much energy"},{"time":401110,"text":"they're saving in real time"},{"time":403074,"text":"makes former speed demons"},{"time":404589,"text":"drive more like cautious grandmothers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":407342,"text":"Which brings us back to Harriet."},{"time":409906,"text":"We met her on our first family vacation."},{"time":412094,"text":"She came over to meet my young daughter,"},{"time":414281,"text":"and she was tickled to learn that my daughter's name"},{"time":416452,"text":"is also Harriet."},{"time":418506,"text":"She asked me what I did for a living,"},{"time":419931,"text":"and I told her, I work with utilities"},{"time":421476,"text":"to help people save energy."},{"time":423352,"text":"It was then that her eyes lit up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":425578,"text":"She looked at me, and she said,"},{"time":427510,"text":"\"You're exactly the person I need to talk to."},{"time":429738,"text":"You see, two weeks ago, my husband and I got a letter"},{"time":431921,"text":"in the mail from our utility."},{"time":434241,"text":"It told us we were using twice as much energy as our neighbors.\""},{"time":437439,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":440869,"text":"\"And for the last two weeks, all we can think about,"},{"time":443689,"text":"talk about, and even argue about,"},{"time":445977,"text":"is what we should be doing to save energy."},{"time":447697,"text":"We did everything that letter told us to do,"},{"time":450562,"text":"and still I know there must be more."},{"time":453364,"text":"Now I'm here with a genuine expert."},{"time":455042,"text":"Tell me. What should I do to save energy?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":459801,"text":"There are many experts who can help answer Harriet's question."},{"time":463853,"text":"My goal is to make sure"},{"time":465915,"text":"we are all asking it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":468213,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":469571,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}